title: Mr. Monster's Hi-Octane Horror (Rumor -Eclipse - 1986)
description:
Stories and art by Michael T. Gilbert, Jerry Grandenetti, George Evans and Basil Wolverton. Cover by Michael T. Gilbert. Reprints of classic stories from the golden age of horror comics, including a Basil Wolverton three-pager. The Secret Files of Dr. Drew; The Man Who Never Smiled; The Metamorphosis of the Gkmloooms. Includes an introduction by Mr. Monster. Sometimes listed as Mr. Monsters Super Duper Special #2.
